    <briefdescription>
<para>Timing Measurement APIs. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>The timing measurement APIs can be used to obtain execution time of a section of code to aid in analysis and optimization.</para>
<para>Please note that the timing functions may use a different timer than the default kernel timer, where the timer being used is specified by architecture, SoC or board configuration. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
